{"tid":878011,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[怪面]有無人好細個陣一合埋眼就見到古怪野?","createTime":"2018-10-26T18:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T01:32:47.000Z","uid":128109,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d3138d0be4a7a6aa7ca4ffe288a01b3b96777999","tid":878011,"uid":128109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T18:53:40.000Z","msg":"是咁的，岩岩小弟冥想嘅時間突然間醒起細過封左塵嘅記憶。我好記得細個個陣時，應該十歲都未到，經常係夜晚個陣時比恐懼困擾。<br />\n<br />\n我次次訓搞個陣一合埋眼就有好多鬼面閃過。有個鬼面記憶猶深，成個頭係死灰色，插滿密密麻麻嘅針，好猙獰咁望住我。下一刻就換過另一個鬼面，各有特色。<br />\n<br />\n我當年以為係我做錯事發惡夢姐，直至我細我幾年嘅細佬突然問我呀媽，『點解耶穌係我訓教個陣時會比D鬼我睇？』，我就知原來唔係得我一個係咁。(天主教家庭大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n我而家諗返去咁細個咁鬼童真，應該未有鬼怪嘅概念，點解我腦海會浮現呢D野？關我前世今生中陰身事？係咪出世前嘅世界留低嘅記憶？有無巴絲細個有類似古怪野？<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 夜晚mediation 好似好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a468967a2b318f3b59128e3b656337df4a6c9c4f","tid":878011,"uid":128109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3138d0be4a7a6aa7ca4ffe288a01b3b96777999","tid":878011,"uid":128109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T18:53:40.000Z","msg":"是咁的，岩岩小弟冥想嘅時間突然間醒起細過封左塵嘅記憶。我好記得細個個陣時，應該十歲都未到，經常係夜晚個陣時比恐懼困擾。<br />\n<br />\n我次次訓搞個陣一合埋眼就有好多鬼面閃過。有個鬼面記憶猶深，成個頭係死灰色，插滿密密麻麻嘅針，好猙獰咁望住我。下一刻就換過另一個鬼面，各有特色。<br />\n<br />\n我當年以為係我做錯事發惡夢姐，直至我細我幾年嘅細佬突然問我呀媽，『點解耶穌係我訓教個陣時會比D鬼我睇？』，我就知原來唔係得我一個係咁。(天主教家庭大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n我而家諗返去咁細個咁鬼童真，應該未有鬼怪嘅概念，點解我腦海會浮現呢D野？關我前世今生中陰身事？係咪出世前嘅世界留低嘅記憶？有無巴絲細個有類似古怪野？<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 夜晚mediation 好似好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T19:19:24.000Z","msg":"*meditation <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f01d1a6381332562ac48f10aaf92766fd7204964","tid":878011,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T19:27:41.000Z","msg":"樓主又會無啦啦記起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97f5483f480f4e80f03ef8768c9abd1930c9964","tid":878011,"uid":137453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T19:43:25.000Z","msg":"有冇同細佬討論過？"},{"pid":"794c8eb3b808fb4ce745e86b0d0fc27976fa6ae3","tid":878011,"uid":200920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T19:50:41.000Z","msg":"我都係 以前細個有排成日失眠 一合埋眼就會有啲紅色黑色既鬼怪面同神佛頭係腦海中出現 好似依啲👉🏻👹"},{"pid":"ae2ca8933c5e2eb6a42bde65ff78fd86848bf0b7","tid":878011,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T19:55:54.000Z","msg":"耶撚未聽過咩叫發惡夢？"},{"pid":"21b0e7c8f69dd11da5fcb12e3f0f2e6408875afe","tid":878011,"uid":43901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T21:53:43.000Z","msg":"我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到有鬼頭上下上下咁漂<br />\n然後周圍都係唔同嘅鬼"},{"pid":"34d53d6d77f079bbea3f9ac7c3fdcdba8c4557b2","tid":878011,"uid":180035,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T22:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQPHieT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQPHieT.jpg&h=4c58bcd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366ee9b0870bae174c9c88ef030fa9eda18dd48f","tid":878011,"uid":109245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34d53d6d77f079bbea3f9ac7c3fdcdba8c4557b2","tid":878011,"uid":180035,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T22:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQPHieT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQPHieT.jpg&h=4c58bcd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T22:42:57.000Z","msg":"hellraiser<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b65b1de3e1444966ab216e6d14175047a3a755","tid":878011,"uid":199352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T23:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個嗰陣 有次表哥帶住我去fd屋企通宵打機 我睇佢地打到一半開始覺得攰 想瞓覺<br />\n但我一合埋眼就見到好多唔同顏色嘅點同線條（大個啲先知係俾光殘住殘住嘅痕跡）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我就同表哥講 我見到有嘢飄下飄下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢同佢個fd本身打緊三國無雙 聽完我講之後 個樣即刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後趕左我去瞓覺 同我講合埋眼就見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5164370cc526407ee6d75f7c153b24371b039d","tid":878011,"uid":100016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T23:58:52.000Z","msg":"依家d on9細個睇完恐怖片發惡夢又可以怪力亂神，智撚障"},{"pid":"c99f142681dc0bd63e6bed773de3d689edd4e1d8","tid":878011,"uid":128109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f01d1a6381332562ac48f10aaf92766fd7204964","tid":878011,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T19:27:41.000Z","msg":"樓主又會無啦啦記起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:28:47.000Z","msg":"打坐個陣時會有好多古舊記憶係浮返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201f6cf610e6e76893c94cc80cedaa80da2f52ab","tid":878011,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:32:47.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦，你唔係普通人，係被選中既小朋友，你天生異稟，有靈力，好撚型啊"}]}